00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:04,080
Lesson 41

2
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:06,950
Penny's bag

3
00:00:06,950 --> 00:00:13,300
Listen to the tape then answer this question.

4
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:18,610
Who is the tin of tobacco for?

5
00:00:18,610 --> 00:00:21,090
Is that bag heavy, Penny?

6
00:00:21,090 --> 00:00:22,950
Not very.

7
00:00:22,950 --> 00:00:24,070
Here!

8
00:00:24,070 --> 00:00:26,490
Put it on this chair.

9
00:00:26,490 --> 00:00:28,230
What's in it?

10
00:00:28,230 --> 00:00:30,660
A piece of cheese.

11
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:32,760
A loaf of bread.

12
00:00:32,760 --> 00:00:34,730
A bar of soap.

13
00:00:34,730 --> 00:00:36,990
A bar of chocolate.

14
00:00:36,990 --> 00:00:39,240
A bottle of milk.

15
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:41,970
A pound of sugar.

16
00:00:41,970 --> 00:00:44,800
Half a pound of coffee.

17
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:47,470
A quarter of a pound of tea.

18
00:00:47,470 --> 00:00:50,230
And a tin of tobacco.

19
00:00:50,230 --> 00:00:52,710
Is that tin of tobacco for me?

20
00:00:52,710 --> 00:00:53,710
Well, it's certainly not for me!
